    "description": "A small robot has to move around a space station, but it can't do it without receiving inputs. <br>Help him by making him avoid obstacles that would send him to certain death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749260/extras/95675e63d39aa5ee1cded459255e2ef6.avif?t=1632947683\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br>String Rush is a puzzle-platformer where you don't control your avatar in real time, but you have to enter the movement commands (input) inside a string and execute them all together. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749260/extras/db5cf8bbe548b424b1becc9dd0d63b06.webp?t=1632947683\" width=317 height=60 /></span><br>► There are currently <strong>26 levels available</strong>, with various types of obstacles. <br>► Each level has <strong>rewards </strong>if you manage to complete it with as few inputs as possible and with only one string. <br>► At least<strong> one hour of playtime</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749260/extras/f320d77516893e97dff4c421259a826a.webp?t=1632947683\" width=441 height=60 /></span><br>This is a solo project (with the exception of some assets that i purchased on unity asset store and some sfx from freesound).<br>I'd like to make many more levels (or maybe make it endless), but this will depend on the interest in the project.<br>In any case, thanks for visiting this page and good gaming!",
